title: RealArcade - Insider Tales The Stolen Venus - New Hidden Object
description:
Insider Tales The Stolen Venus
  

Biggest art robbery in decades: Botticelli's masterpiece stolen!
Just yesterday there were hundreds of art loving visitors elbowing their way
through the crowd to have a glimpse at the masterpiece, today only the frame on a bare wall awaits.Help inspector Francesca Di Porta solve her case in this mysterious hidden object game
with an intriguing story of suspicion, prosecution and conspiracy!
